  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Aliskiren and Atenolol in Adults (&gt;18) With Mild to Moderate Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Twelve-week, Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel-group, Multicenter, Dose Escalation Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Aliskiren Administered Alone and in Combination With Atenolol in Patients With Essential Hypertension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
